title: Eps. 175 - Tobe's Turn
description:
Today’s podcast features Tobe Nwigwe as he shares his journey on how’s he’s been able to achieve an incredible level of stardom. The theme for today’s show is “Take The Stairs”. Many people want to obtain success and keep it, but they believe there is a shortcut. A myth that Tobe denounces. This conversation is for anyone who’s trying to build something from the ground up. The underlying theme of today’s episode is to be consistent with your gift/skillset, grab your pens and pads, get ready to take notes.
